Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我乃征服王伊斯坎達爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於此次聖杯戰爭  以Rider職階現身人間！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在想什麼啊  你這個笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然此次是與汝等互相爭奪聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我想先詢問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可有意入我麾下  將聖杯相讓於我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有此意  我則視汝等為友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一同分享征服世界的愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我難以接受這個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要為之獻上聖杯的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在此生與我立下契約的新任君主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.28,0:01:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而絕非是你啊  Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你就只是為了來說如此戲言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.37,0:01:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不惜擾亂我與Lancer的決鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.02,0:01:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於騎士來說  這是難以饒恕的侮辱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待遇問題可以商量的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.95,0:01:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外要強調的是  我也是統治不列顛的一國之君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕你是多麼偉大的君王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不會俯首稱臣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  原來是不列顛王？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.39,0:01:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名滿天下的騎士王竟是一個小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就吃你所說的這個小姑娘一劍如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.24,0:01:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征服王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來談判破裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可惜了  真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rider！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾差點征服世界的就是這麼一個笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  居然偏偏是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還在想你究竟是犯了什麼邪去偷了我的聖遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是你自己想來參加聖杯戰爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韋伯·威爾維特同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要我特意為你來一次課外輔導呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔術師之間的廝殺意味著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及其中的恐怖與痛苦  我會毫無保留地教給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此感到光榮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  魔術師！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看樣子你曾想代替這小子成為我的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是讓人笑掉大牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能成為我Master的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得是能與我並肩馳騁于疆場的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種連面都不敢露的膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就不夠格！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  還有其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些潛伏在黑暗中窺視這裡的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是什麼意思  Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber  還有Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝等堂堂正正的對決很是精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此清澈的劍戟交擊之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所引來的英靈應該不只我一個才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被聖杯所召喚的英靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在便集結於此處吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對那些害怕被人看到的膽小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我征服王伊斯坎達爾可不會有一絲尊重！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒了Assassin的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到  不經本王許可就妄自稱王的無禮之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一夜之間就冒出來兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這指責真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我伊斯坎達爾  就是世人皆知的征服王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑話  真正稱得上王的英雄  天上天下唯我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的都是一堆堆不像樣的雜種
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然敢如此放話  那先報上你的大名如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你也是個夠格稱王的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會忌憚於說出自己的名號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問我的名號？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這雜種竟敢在本王面前問名號？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受著能覲見本王的榮耀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻說不識本王的面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種愚昧小人怎配活在這個世上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  他就是用那東西幹掉Assassin的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是…他的寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  征服王  你要邀請那傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說什麼邀請了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得一開始就沒有和他交涉的餘地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子  那傢伙作為Servant究竟有何種程度的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法判斷  根本無法判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  你勉強也算是個Master
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總應該看得出能力強弱之類的東西吧  嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個黑傢伙毫無疑問就是Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不管是狀態還是其他都完全無法讀取…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來那也是個棘手的敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.75,0:08:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來那個英靈有著能隱藏身份的特殊能力或者詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅如此  同時和四個敵人對峙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就無法貿然行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在這個時候實體化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡是有正常思維的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種毫無戰略可言的混亂之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不會想出特意讓Servant現身的下策
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞彌  你繼續監視Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這邊搜索Berserker的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰允許你抬頭看我的  瘋狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起碼用你的淒慘死狀來取悅於我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雜種！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙真的是Berserker嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一個因狂化而失去理性的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這技巧實在出眾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼  你沒看出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個黑傢伙輕易地抓住了先到的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將緊隨其後的槍擊飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢用你那雙髒手碰我的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼急著想死嗎？瘋狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:10:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看  你靠這讓人不快的小偷手段能撐多久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大膽狂徒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢讓本應如同天空一樣被人仰視的本王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與你同立於大地之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此不敬實乃罪該萬死！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的雜種  我要你灰飛煙滅！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾伽美什是動真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來還想進一步釋放「王之財寶」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(840,650)\fs40}Gate  of  Babylon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然將必殺寶具屢次暴露在眾目睽睽之下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太輕率了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.57,0:11:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師  請下決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以令咒諫之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄王  請平息怒火  撤離戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑你的進諫  就想讓本王撤退？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的譜擺得真大啊  時臣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算你撿了一條命  瘋狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雜種們  就繼續演你們的鬧劇去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需和真正的英雄一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來那傢伙的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性格並不如Archer本人一般剛毅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗斯菲爾  快後退！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那黑傢伙無論拿起什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能將其變成自己的寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  舞彌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從你那邊能看到Berserker的Master嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…究竟是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惡作劇就請到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的Saber可是跟我有約在先
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你還想攪局的話  我可不會坐視不理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancer…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什麼  Lancer？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打倒Saber  現在正是好機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迪爾梅德·奧迪納以榮譽保證  定將Saber斃於槍下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如若不信  我可以先解決這只瘋狗給您看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還望恩准  我的主君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以令咒命之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主君！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去掩護Berserker  將Saber…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗斯菲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡由我來拖住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起碼能讓你趁此機會逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跑多遠就跑多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗斯菲爾  快！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會有事的  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要相信你的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣他已經來這裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切嗣  你一定能夠反敗為勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在  我要將Lancer的Master狙殺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打破眼下這困局  除此以外別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞彌  聽我的倒數向Assassin發起攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火力壓制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙骨頭還真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我請那黑傢伙退場了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancer的Master啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道你究竟在哪裡偷看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我絕不許你用卑鄙手段來玷污騎士的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓Lancer退下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你想再讓他蒙羞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將會與Saber聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:17:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時候可就是我們兩人齊上打倒你的Servant了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.94,0:17:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你意下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退  Lancer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征服王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡的話  戰場之花可得好生呵護不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來  你究竟是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,征服王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  這種事情就別太過計較了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber  你先跟Lancer把帳算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那時候  我再跟勝利的一個對決
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣吧  騎士王  先就此別過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下次見面之時  再讓我好好熱血沸騰一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小子  不來說幾句帥氣的臺詞麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能稍微像樣點嗎  這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber  左手怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很慘重的失態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如Rider所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不先跟Lancer分出勝負  解除傷口的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會影響和其他Servant的對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了你  我才能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以能夠勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是因為有你守在我的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負才剛剛開始  愛麗蘇斯爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是即將拉開帷幕的戰爭的第一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們都是真正的強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有一人是泛泛之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…聖杯戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的Berserker面前夾起尾巴逃跑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於讓那不可一世的傢伙顏面掃地了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時臣  我真想看看你氣急敗壞的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker這混蛋  竟然向著Saber發起瘋來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後要還是這樣的話  我的身體可會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要可以駕馭…就能做到！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我打擾  綺禮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  在教會外面  發現了讓人在意的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特來稟報
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是使魔麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是在結界之外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但屬下認為明顯是為了監視這教會才佈置的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊  真的好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍鬍子老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些  都是真的對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是電影特效也不是其他什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是真的對不？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  那是叫「聖杯戰爭」來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺你也參加了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實現了？  我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那威風凜凜的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那神聖不可侵犯的英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正是如假包換的  我命中註定的少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾經被上帝所拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在屈辱中死去的她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今  終於復活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣…這樣的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只可能是我的願望終於實現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的聖女…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就來迎接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.68,0:23:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必會斬下Saber的項上人頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次我絕不會手下留情！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞錯了的是你才對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受一下凱納斯·埃爾梅羅的魔術工房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想對我說教？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.66,0:23:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來迎接您了  聖女
